Section: python
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${python:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, python-restauth-common
XB-Python-Version: ${python:Versions}
Provides: ${python:Provides}
Description: client library for RestAuth webservices
 This library is written in pure Python and is a reference implementation of
 the RestAuth protocol.

